title: 'GM Street' — Eli Manning's Benching, Tennessee's Coaching Vacancy, and Joe Flacco's Floundering (Ep. 192)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier discuss Ben McAdoo's decision to bench Eli Manning (01:00), Joe Flacco's check-down routine (18:15), Miami's many struggles (33:30), and the college football coaching carousel (42:00).
